net.openhft.chronicle.bytes

Enum NoBytesStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NoBytesStore>
      • net.openhft.chronicle.bytes.NoBytesStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CharSequence, Comparable<NoBytesStore>, BytesStore, RandomDataInput, RandomDataOutput, net.openhft.chronicle.core.io.ReferenceCounted, net.openhft.chronicle.core.io.ReferenceOwner

    public enum NoBytesStore
extends Enum<NoBytesStore>
implements BytesStore
    This is a ByteStore which uses no space but could be resized to be larger (by replacing it with a ByteStire with space)
    See Also:
    ReleasedBytesStore
